snippet.title: Dev Diaries: Caves & Cliffs Mobs
snippet.description: Join Cory, Chi, and Nir for a closer look at the mobs that are joining Minecraft in the Caves & Cliffs update! Learn about the work that went into the goat jumping mechanic, get the backstory on the endangered axolotl Easter egg, and discover ways to craft with glow ink sacks. You think that’s a lot of information? Well, it’s because we ask a lot’l questions!
